<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Welcome to {{ item.name }}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            width: 35em;
            margin: 0 auto;
            font-family: Tahoma, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 0;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #666;
        }
        .success {
            color: #4CAF50;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to {{ item.name }}</h1>
        <p>If you see this page, the Nginx web server is successfully installed and
        working. Further configuration is required.</p>

        <p class="success">Your LEMP stack is running!</p>

        <p>Server details:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Operating System: Ubuntu 24.04</li>
            <li>Web Server: Nginx {{ nginx_version }}</li>
            <li>PHP Version: {{ item.php_version | default(default_php_version) }}</li>
            <li>Database: Percona {{ percona_version }}</li>
        </ul>

        <p><em>Thank you for using the Ansible LEMP Stack installer.</em></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 